    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this masterfully preserved vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits no signs of wear, featuring an unblemished exterior finish and an interior that remains in factory-fresh state. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a truly superlative example of automotive excellence. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are beyond reproach.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
