    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, showroom condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including professional VANOS servicing and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The chassis retains its original rigidity with OEM-spec bushings and a perfectly tuned MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of clear coat failure or road rash, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A mechanically peerless example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents. Clean title. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents a true 'time-capsule' find, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster free of stone chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom; the premium leather is supple and entirely uncreased, the carpets are pristine, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate seat adjustments, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service log and a whisper-quiet engine that delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to acquire a collector-grade specimen that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
